HEADWORD: Illtreat
<hw>Ill`treat"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To treat cruelly
or improperly; to ill use; to maltreat.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> mistreat, maltreat, abuse, ill-use.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

